# Rule: Import Colors from Figma via MCP

At no point should you add any new files to the project, except when asked to 'add a new file'.

## Import the Color Design Tokens from Figma via MCP

- Use the `.cursor/mcp/figma-links.yaml` file to get the Figma link of the colors section.
- Remove the existing theme colors in the file `src/sass/root/_colors.scss` and add the colors from the provided link. Do not touch any of the semantic colors. Add the values as RGBA values.
